source/OpenAI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OpenAI\"}, {\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9055478953007634e-17, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Generative AIis\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 199}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"major corporations\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"a stake\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 326}, {\"ngram\": \"the landscape\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the technology has raised many question marks among users centered on privacy, security, and its capability to spread misinformation and deepfakes.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the technology\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"many question marks\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"users\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"privacy\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"its capability\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"misinformation\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"deepfakes\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last bit is perhaps increasingly becoming a major threat with the elections edging close, coupled with the lack of tools and measures to help identifyAI-generated deepfakes and misinformation.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last bit\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"a major threat\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"the elections\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"tools\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"measures\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"identifyAI-generated deepfakes\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"misinformation\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the case with Russian-based influencers reportedly leveraging AI tech to spread misinformation about the 2024 Paris Olympics (viaThe Hill).\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3391038577576475e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"Russian-based influencers\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"misinformation\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"viaThe Hill\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to areportby Microsoft's Threat Analysis Center, Russian actors have been leveraging the technology's capabilities to ruin the reputation of the International Olympic Committee (IOC) by spreading fear about violence at the Olympic Games via AI-generated videos, articles, and images.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.99999330002145, \"rank\": 6.700012794056478e-06, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}, {\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998534785823721, \"rank\": 0.00014616626428650456, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the technology's capabilities\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the reputation\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"AI-generated videos\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"articles\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, Russian actor Storm-1679 leveraged AI to create a fake documentary on Netflix with a voice reminiscent of veteran actor Tom Cruise that presented the IOC in a bad light.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998534785823721, \"rank\": 0.00014616626428650456, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3391038577576475e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.999999999145075, \"rank\": 8.545