ime was factored into the project, ultimately demonstrating \\\"more skill than most influence campaigns.\\\"\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.99999330002145, \"rank\": 6.700012794056478e-06, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"special effects\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"an illusion\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"more skill\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"most influence campaigns\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the threat actor has used the technology to generate fake news branded as 'reliable' from well-known sources like Euro News or France24.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_24\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France24\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_24\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_24\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the threat actor\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the technology\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"fake news\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"well-known sources\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"Euro News\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian actor used these avenues as platforms to spread malicious lies, purporting that Paris is worried about the potential violence that could stem from the upcoming Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998534785823721, \"rank\": 0.00014616626428650456, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973597369, \"rank\": 2.6404235798741896e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these avenues\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"platforms\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"malicious lies\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential violence\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, Storm-1679 created fake videos that it presented as belonging to the CIA, urging people to stay away from the Olympic Games over terrorism concerns.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Information_security\", \"score\": 0.9993259888487185, \"rank\": 0.0006744657368522737, \"text\": \"CIA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Information_security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Information_security\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Storm-1679\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"fake videos\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorism concerns\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actors have 